{"tid":713541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國李寧登陸巴黎變「潮流」品牌？網民：配埋「祝君安好」毛巾如虎添翼","createTime":"2018-06-23T01:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T03:28:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d16c832bad7411eab4257cc1740da137ba2e7b","tid":713541,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T01:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2100000/2100333/0_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2100000%2F2100333%2F0_1024.jpg&h=ff896fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大部份香港人，都對中國大陸的運動用品品牌不太感興趣，大概認為不是山寨，就是不夠時尚。怎樣想也好，李寧牌早前宣布，會在法國巴黎展出 2019 春夏系列產品，氣勢有如潮流品牌一樣，同時模特兒行天橋的相片亦剛剛發布，教不少人吃了一驚。其中一個系列，更以白底紅字印上「中國李寧」4 個大字，有網民譏諷：「配埋『祝君安好』毛巾簡直係如虎添翼。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2100000/2100333/3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2100000%2F2100333%2F3_600.jpg&h=dd67d901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稍早前李寧牌表示，會在巴黎時間 2018 年 6 月 21 日，攜 2019 春夏系列產品亮相巴黎。新一季大秀將以「中國李寧」作為主題，以李寧運動員生涯的盛世傳奇為靈感，以未來視角解讀 90 年代復古經典運動潮流，旨在展現品牌於經典之中傳承而來的深厚積澱，傳遞了中國李寧堅守之中的全新蛻變，致敬未來的無限可能。本次中國李寧的巴黎之行，將憑借其獨特的東方印記，再次向世界傳遞中國創造的強勢聲音，展望經典傳奇的無限未來，一切皆有可能！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2100000/2100333/4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2100000%2F2100333%2F4_600.jpg&h=a9ff308e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說到底，究竟是怎麼一回呢？這一兩天，謎底終於揭曉。其中最「搶眼」的一個系列，衣服上半位置，便以白底紅字印上「中國李寧」4 個大字，令不少香港網民議論紛紛，留言包括：「今次真係連陳冠希都 carry 唔到」、「完美示範何為柒到盡頭便是型」、「竟然唔係殘體字，侮辱國家樽鹽」等，不過也有人認為其實不是太差：「呢個 style 外國人應該鍾意，Btw，我唔會買」、「公平 D 咁講，其實同 Supreme 差不多， 話佢醜，其實 Supreme 都一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2100333/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9D%8E%E5%AF%A7%E7%99%BB%E9%99%B8%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%E6%BD%AE%E6%B5%81%E3%80%8D%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%9F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E9%85%8D%E5%9F%8B%E3%80%8C%E7%A5%9D%E5%90%9B%E5%AE%89%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%8D%E6%AF%9B%E5%B7%BE%E5%A6%82%E8%99%8E%E6%B7%BB%E7%BF%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2100333%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AF%25A7%25E7%2599%25BB%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E8%25AE%258A%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E6%25B5%2581%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25EF%25BC%259F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%2585%258D%25E5%259F%258B%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A5%259D%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25AF%259B%25E5%25B7%25BE%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%2599%258E%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E7%25BF%25BC&d=QtpeFnbj0S7RMojtUuuwcv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=60e50f10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2100333/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9D%8E%E5%AF%A7%E7%99%BB%E9%99%B8%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%E6%BD%AE%E6%B5%81%E3%80%8D%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%9F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E9%85%8D%E5%9F%8B%E3%80%8C%E7%A5%9D%E5%90%9B%E5%AE%89%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%8D%E6%AF%9B%E5%B7%BE%E5%A6%82%E8%99%8E%E6%B7%BB%E7%BF%BC</a>"},{"pid":"209e63bf0565c96d97ba7d37767437879506bc63","tid":713541,"uid":45368,"like":365,"dislike":2,"score":363,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「公平 D 咁講，其實同 Supreme 差不多， 話佢醜，其實 Supreme 都一樣。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又無撚講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9586a691c18e144b2e975284677d6b91eab276ae","tid":713541,"uid":61954,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:00:00.000Z","msg":"柒到盡頭還是柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj